  "title": "Customer Service Engineer/Technician - Printers (Up to $3900) #NKA",
  "description": "<p>Location: Pasir Panjang (Need to be comfortable travelling around Singapore depending on business needs)<br /></p><p><strong>Duration:</strong> 1 year contract<br /></p><p><strong>Working Hours:</strong> Mon - Fri, 8:45am - 5:45pm (or similar staggered timing depending on customers' site)<br /></p><p><strong>Salary: </strong>Up to $3900<br /><br /><br /><strong>Job Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li>Carry out installation, repair and preventive maintenance of customers’ MFDs (e.g. copiers and printers)</li><li>Manage the inventory of MFD parts, tools and assets assigned to you</li><li>Ensure internal records are updated timely and status of service calls are communicated to the team</li></ul><p><strong></strong><br /><strong>Job Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Experience in troubleshooting monochrome and colour printers in a network environment</li><li>Good interpersonal skills and the ability to work in a team</li></ul><p></p><p>Ally<br />The Outsourcing Team<br />Recruit Express Pte Ltd<br />EA: 99C4599</p><p></p>",
